<Speech gate:gateId="110753" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="109076" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="111251" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="109819" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="109574" majorType="speaker">Χρήστος Μαρκογιαννάκης</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Ορίστε, συνεχίστε.</Speech></Speech>
